{"tid":1033688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"任正非:感謝特朗普推廣華為","createTime":"2019-02-23T11:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T12:44:04.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0693f4aa941bc73f6c4c7e9c590a6bd475c4fd","tid":1033688,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2019/02/23/2065524_6f1b3f90b778e4b260efb1b4e958440e_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2019%2F02%2F23%2F2065524_6f1b3f90b778e4b260efb1b4e958440e_320.jpg&h=728da8a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n華為創辦人任正非接受美國哥倫比亞廣播公司訪問時表示，5G不是原子彈，又感謝美國總統特朗普及副總統彭斯(Mike Pence)為華為作推廣，也因此獲得更多合同。<br />\n<br />\n被問到特朗普政府對使用華為設備的盟友發出警告，彭斯也在慕尼黑安全會議上稱，盟友愈來愈依賴東方國家，就無法確保西方國家的安全。任正非回應稱，他們兩個都是大人物，5G技術此前並不為大眾熟知，但現在這些大人物都在談論5G，華為變得更有影響力，也因此獲得了更多的合同。<br />\n<br />\n他又要求記者轉告兩人，實際上是在感謝他們推廣了華為。<br />\n<br />\n任正非又指出，美國政府把5G技術誇大到某些軍事設施的水平，但5G不是原子彈，華為現推出5G，很快還將迎來6G。在未來，將會有適合美國的新設備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2065524/%E4%BB%BB%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%9E%3A%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fchina%2Farticle%2F2065524%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E9%259D%259E%253A%25E6%2584%259F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1AV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=927450f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/china/article/2065524/%E4%BB%BB%E6%AD%A3%E9%9D%9E%3A%E6%84%9F%E8%AC%9D%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%8E%A8%E5%BB%A3%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA</a>"},{"pid":"87dd6f32f5977bbd2ed83b527b1018d4a6c0232e","tid":1033688,"uid":44454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:36:11.000Z","msg":"好事成雙，拉埋個細女啦"},{"pid":"cfc77d3713f8484bf7f855bf7ebbdbdcf3a77191"